WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:18.588 align:middle line:90%


00:00:18.588 --> 00:00:22.040 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA GARR: Hi, I'm Lisa Garr,
host of "Gaiam Inspirations."

00:00:22.040 --> 00:00:24.060 align:middle line:84%
We are coming to you live
from the Gaiam studios

00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:25.180 align:middle line:90%
here in Boulder, Colorado.

00:00:25.180 --> 00:00:27.240 align:middle line:84%
And since this is a
live show, I encourage

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:29.740 align:middle line:84%
you to interact with me
via Facebook and Twitter.

00:00:29.740 --> 00:00:31.740 align:middle line:84%
We encourage your questions
throughout the show.

00:00:31.740 --> 00:00:34.370 align:middle line:84%
And we will be asking the
guests questions as well.

00:00:34.370 --> 00:00:37.480 align:middle line:84%
So you see the bumper
stickers on the cars that say,

00:00:37.480 --> 00:00:38.740 align:middle line:90%
create world peace.

00:00:38.740 --> 00:00:41.200 align:middle line:84%
And you've seen
the Occupy Movement

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:42.750 align:middle line:90%
rush across the country.

00:00:42.750 --> 00:00:46.240 align:middle line:84%
But what is really
being done right now?

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:48.650 align:middle line:84%
What's really being done
about our current economic and

00:00:48.650 --> 00:00:50.430 align:middle line:90%
environmental structures?

00:00:50.430 --> 00:00:53.060 align:middle line:84%
Are we moving towards
a global domination?

00:00:53.060 --> 00:00:55.900 align:middle line:84%
And if we are, what
can we do about it?

00:00:55.900 --> 00:00:57.620 align:middle line:84%
That's what we're
talking about today.

00:00:57.620 --> 00:01:00.310 align:middle line:84%
Experts say that awareness
is 80% of the solution.

00:01:00.310 --> 00:01:02.440 align:middle line:84%
And today we're talking
about solutions.

00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:06.210 align:middle line:84%
Joining me are Foster Gamble
and Kimberly Carter Gamble.

00:01:06.210 --> 00:01:08.410 align:middle line:84%
And they are the
visionary filmmakers

00:01:08.410 --> 00:01:12.170 align:middle line:84%
of the movie "Thrive" which is
an inspirational documentary

00:01:12.170 --> 00:01:13.910 align:middle line:90%
that raises so much awareness.

00:01:13.910 --> 00:01:17.170 align:middle line:84%
But most importantly, it
brings about solutions.

00:01:17.170 --> 00:01:19.250 align:middle line:84%
Thank you both very
much for being here.

00:01:19.250 --> 00:01:20.834 align:middle line:90%
Incredible film.

00:01:20.834 --> 00:01:22.500 align:middle line:84%
Millions of people
have already seen it.

00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:24.390 align:middle line:90%
It's offered here on Gaiam TV.

00:01:24.390 --> 00:01:26.210 align:middle line:84%
How long did it take
you to make this film?

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:27.344 align:middle line:90%


00:01:27.344 --> 00:01:29.760 align:middle line:84%
>>KIMBERLY CARTER GAMBLE: It
actually took us eight years.

00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:31.634 align:middle line:84%
Eight years to make the
film and the website.

00:01:31.634 --> 00:01:34.169 align:middle line:84%
Really there's a super
comprehensive website,

00:01:34.169 --> 00:01:34.960 align:middle line:90%
thrivemovement.com.

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:36.315 align:middle line:90%


00:01:36.315 --> 00:01:38.505 align:middle line:84%
In a lot of ways
we've said the movie

00:01:38.505 --> 00:01:40.510 align:middle line:90%
is a trailer for the website.

00:01:40.510 --> 00:01:42.700 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And it's
a two hour movie.

00:01:42.700 --> 00:01:43.640 align:middle line:90%
It's a long trailer.

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.470 align:middle line:84%
>>K. GAMBLE: It's
quite comprehensive.

00:01:44.470 --> 00:01:46.480 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But what was
the vision behind it?

00:01:46.480 --> 00:01:48.170 align:middle line:84%
Why did you need
to create something

00:01:48.170 --> 00:01:51.311 align:middle line:84%
like this that brought about so
much awareness and solutions?

00:01:51.311 --> 00:01:53.560 align:middle line:84%
>>FOSTER GAMBLE: My answer
would probably be 50 years.

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:54.600 align:middle line:90%


00:01:54.600 --> 00:01:58.030 align:middle line:84%
Because it really has been a
lifelong pursuit and then dream

00:01:58.030 --> 00:02:00.500 align:middle line:84%
come true for me to
finally get this film out.

00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:02.230 align:middle line:84%
Because, as I
described in the film,

00:02:02.230 --> 00:02:05.350 align:middle line:84%
I had a vision when I was
14 of a fundamental energy

00:02:05.350 --> 00:02:06.920 align:middle line:90%
pattern of the universe.

00:02:06.920 --> 00:02:09.680 align:middle line:84%
And the teacher that I
told about this vision

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:12.030 align:middle line:84%
had the wisdom to say, wow,
what an interesting idea.

00:02:12.030 --> 00:02:14.474 align:middle line:84%
Keep going on that, and let
me know what you come up with.

00:02:14.474 --> 00:02:16.390 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know it would
be the rest of my life.

00:02:16.390 --> 00:02:18.790 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Did you see pictures
in your mind of this, or--

00:02:18.790 --> 00:02:20.410 align:middle line:84%
>>F. GAMBLE: No, I was
riding on a school bus

00:02:20.410 --> 00:02:21.620 align:middle line:90%
and looking out the window.

00:02:21.620 --> 00:02:23.620 align:middle line:84%
And I think the light
blinking through the trees

00:02:23.620 --> 00:02:26.830 align:middle line:84%
probably helped put me in
a somewhat altered state.

00:02:26.830 --> 00:02:29.270 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden
there was this whirlpool

00:02:29.270 --> 00:02:32.910 align:middle line:84%
that I was seeing, as if
it were out in the air.

00:02:32.910 --> 00:02:35.560 align:middle line:84%
And then I was seeing an
atom in the middle of it.

00:02:35.560 --> 00:02:37.700 align:middle line:84%
Then the atom transformed
into a solar system

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:40.210 align:middle line:84%
so I was seeing the
similarity between those.

00:02:40.210 --> 00:02:42.930 align:middle line:84%
And then I got a
whole body sense

00:02:42.930 --> 00:02:45.550 align:middle line:84%
that somehow I was
that same pattern.

00:02:45.550 --> 00:02:47.630 align:middle line:84%
That remained a mystery
to me for a long time.

00:02:47.630 --> 00:02:49.461 align:middle line:84%
But it gets addressed
in the film.

00:02:49.461 --> 00:02:51.710 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It gives me chills
just to hear you talk about

00:02:51.710 --> 00:02:54.061 align:middle line:84%
that because that was a real
vision that came through

00:02:54.061 --> 00:02:54.560 align:middle line:90%
to you.

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:58.140 align:middle line:84%
And you carried it out which
is a story in and of itself.

00:02:58.140 --> 00:03:00.386 align:middle line:84%
But the idea behind
the film-- I want

00:03:00.386 --> 00:03:02.010 align:middle line:84%
you take a look at
this clip because it

00:03:02.010 --> 00:03:04.200 align:middle line:84%
shows the concept
behind the film

00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:06.732 align:middle line:84%
and this energy,
this toroidal energy

00:03:06.732 --> 00:03:07.940 align:middle line:90%
that Foster is talking about.

00:03:07.940 --> 00:03:08.440 align:middle line:90%
Take a look.

00:03:08.440 --> 00:03:09.680 align:middle line:90%
[BEGIN VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:11.560 align:middle line:84%
>>NASSIM HARAMEIN:
These toroidal dynamics

00:03:11.560 --> 00:03:13.980 align:middle line:90%
are visible at various scales.

00:03:13.980 --> 00:03:16.600 align:middle line:84%
One of them is at
the galactic level,

00:03:16.600 --> 00:03:20.390 align:middle line:84%
which are huge spinning
structures with billions

00:03:20.390 --> 00:03:21.890 align:middle line:90%
of stars in it.

00:03:21.890 --> 00:03:29.070 align:middle line:84%
Looks like, typically, big arms
of galaxies spinning around.

00:03:29.070 --> 00:03:30.110 align:middle line:90%


00:03:30.110 --> 00:03:35.910 align:middle line:84%
And they have vortices
that goes from the center

00:03:35.910 --> 00:03:43.450 align:middle line:84%
out to the edge of the galactic
halo that surrounds them.

00:03:43.450 --> 00:03:50.220 align:middle line:84%
Stars move from this galactic
disc out to the halo,

00:03:50.220 --> 00:03:53.700 align:middle line:84%
down the vortices,
and back out again.

00:03:53.700 --> 00:03:56.180 align:middle line:84%
Stars like Arcturus,
for instance,

00:03:56.180 --> 00:03:58.380 align:middle line:84%
we know have done
that path already.

00:03:58.380 --> 00:03:59.780 align:middle line:90%


00:03:59.780 --> 00:04:02.230 align:middle line:84%
That's the appropriate
description

00:04:02.230 --> 00:04:05.710 align:middle line:84%
even for the atmosphere
of our planet.

00:04:05.710 --> 00:04:09.490 align:middle line:84%
The weather goes from the
North Pole down to the equator

00:04:09.490 --> 00:04:10.660 align:middle line:90%
and then back up.

00:04:10.660 --> 00:04:14.500 align:middle line:84%
From the South Pole up to the
equator and then back down.

00:04:14.500 --> 00:04:18.189 align:middle line:84%
Even the dynamics on the surface
of the sun are very similar.

00:04:18.189 --> 00:04:19.380 align:middle line:90%


00:04:19.380 --> 00:04:21.529 align:middle line:84%
Of course here
we're looking at it

00:04:21.529 --> 00:04:25.870 align:middle line:84%
from an external perspective
on a small scale model.

00:04:25.870 --> 00:04:29.655 align:middle line:84%
When you look at the
solar system embedded

00:04:29.655 --> 00:04:35.950 align:middle line:84%
in the galaxy, embedded
in the cluster,

00:04:35.950 --> 00:04:40.378 align:middle line:84%
embedded in the
super cluster, we're

00:04:40.378 --> 00:04:45.790 align:middle line:84%
traveling in this boundless
sea of infinite torus flow.

00:04:45.790 --> 00:04:47.290 align:middle line:90%
[END VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:04:47.290 --> 00:04:50.330 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I particularly love
the visuals in this movie.

00:04:50.330 --> 00:04:52.310 align:middle line:84%
It really helps
represent something

00:04:52.310 --> 00:04:54.085 align:middle line:84%
that we can't see
with the normal eye.

00:04:54.085 --> 00:04:56.660 align:middle line:84%
And you have put
so much into this.

00:04:56.660 --> 00:04:58.407 align:middle line:84%
I love the aesthetics
that it brings.

00:04:58.407 --> 00:04:59.740 align:middle line:90%
It's like a whole 'nother guest.

00:04:59.740 --> 00:05:02.650 align:middle line:84%
>>F. GAMBLE: We really wanted
to help people see in 3D.

00:05:02.650 --> 00:05:05.809 align:middle line:84%
And we've been getting
communications from people

00:05:05.809 --> 00:05:06.600 align:middle line:90%
all over the world.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:12.390 align:middle line:84%
From spiritual communities,
from healers, from growers,

00:05:12.390 --> 00:05:15.670 align:middle line:84%
thanking us for finally
putting into graphics

00:05:15.670 --> 00:05:18.150 align:middle line:84%
what they have been
seeing in their intuition,

00:05:18.150 --> 00:05:20.420 align:middle line:84%
and what they've been
using in their healing,

00:05:20.420 --> 00:05:22.760 align:middle line:84%
and teaching their students,
and so forth for years.

00:05:22.760 --> 00:05:24.370 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So it's really
connecting with people.

00:05:24.370 --> 00:05:24.990 align:middle line:90%
>>F. GAMBLE: Yeah, exactly.

00:05:24.990 --> 00:05:26.130 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Very good.

00:05:26.130 --> 00:05:30.460 align:middle line:84%
Now, once you started seeing
this energy in the universe,

00:05:30.460 --> 00:05:32.395 align:middle line:84%
did you start to see it
everywhere in history?

00:05:32.395 --> 00:05:33.400 align:middle line:90%
Did you look back?

00:05:33.400 --> 00:05:36.220 align:middle line:84%
I mean, was it like
attracting like?

00:05:36.220 --> 00:05:38.340 align:middle line:84%
>>F. GAMBLE: Well, one
thing led to another.

00:05:38.340 --> 00:05:41.370 align:middle line:84%
And I had no idea where
it was going to lead.

00:05:41.370 --> 00:05:45.030 align:middle line:84%
When I came to the realization
with a lot of other scientists

00:05:45.030 --> 00:05:47.070 align:middle line:84%
that I was working
with that this torus

00:05:47.070 --> 00:05:49.380 align:middle line:84%
pattern and the-- what
he calls the vector

00:05:49.380 --> 00:05:53.030 align:middle line:84%
equilibrium structural geometry
that is a pair with it-- when

00:05:53.030 --> 00:05:55.700 align:middle line:84%
we realized that that was
fundamental at all scales,

00:05:55.700 --> 00:05:58.261 align:middle line:84%
I realized that we couldn't be
the first ones to know that.

00:05:58.261 --> 00:06:00.760 align:middle line:84%
And sure enough, as we started
looking back through history,

00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:04.950 align:middle line:84%
and I got educated by people
like Nassim Haramein and Graham

00:06:04.950 --> 00:06:06.780 align:middle line:84%
Hancock and Stan
Tenen and others

00:06:06.780 --> 00:06:08.790 align:middle line:84%
who really looked into
this-- it turns out

00:06:08.790 --> 00:06:12.495 align:middle line:84%
that ancient mystics have
encoded this information

00:06:12.495 --> 00:06:14.689 align:middle line:84%
and actually send
it across millennia.

00:06:14.689 --> 00:06:16.480 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: This is what
I find so fascinating.

00:06:16.480 --> 00:06:17.521 align:middle line:90%
Take a look at this clip.

00:06:17.521 --> 00:06:20.340 align:middle line:84%
You can see where
the torus shows up

00:06:20.340 --> 00:06:21.860 align:middle line:90%
in history, ancient history.

00:06:21.860 --> 00:06:23.604 align:middle line:90%


00:06:23.604 --> 00:06:24.520 align:middle line:90%
[BEGIN VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:26.728 align:middle line:84%
>>F. GAMBLE: Here we are at
one of the world's oldest

00:06:26.728 --> 00:06:30.720 align:middle line:84%
sacred sites, the Osirian
Temple at Abydos, Egypt.

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:31.980 align:middle line:90%


00:06:31.980 --> 00:06:36.280 align:middle line:84%
>>HARAMEIN: Very little writing
is found in the Osirian Temple.

00:06:36.280 --> 00:06:41.030 align:middle line:84%
However, there is one
very significant piece

00:06:41.030 --> 00:06:42.740 align:middle line:90%
of information in that Temple.

00:06:42.740 --> 00:06:44.230 align:middle line:90%


00:06:44.230 --> 00:06:49.740 align:middle line:84%
It is a very faint but
clear and precise drawing.

00:06:49.740 --> 00:06:51.010 align:middle line:90%


00:06:51.010 --> 00:06:55.510 align:middle line:84%
It's not etched into the
rock; it's not carved.

00:06:55.510 --> 00:07:00.010 align:middle line:84%
It's burned into
the atomic structure

00:07:00.010 --> 00:07:03.630 align:middle line:84%
of the rock in some
extraordinary way.

00:07:03.630 --> 00:07:04.870 align:middle line:90%


00:07:04.870 --> 00:07:07.820 align:middle line:84%
>>F. GAMBLE: Nassim has
decoded the Osirian symbol

00:07:07.820 --> 00:07:08.665 align:middle line:90%
in three dimensions.

00:07:08.665 --> 00:07:09.750 align:middle line:90%


00:07:09.750 --> 00:07:12.030 align:middle line:84%
Since our world is
not two-dimensional,

00:07:12.030 --> 00:07:14.410 align:middle line:84%
it makes sense the codes
relaying information

00:07:14.410 --> 00:07:18.350 align:middle line:84%
about our world also wouldn't
be limited to flat designs.

00:07:18.350 --> 00:07:20.090 align:middle line:90%


00:07:20.090 --> 00:07:23.310 align:middle line:84%
His three-dimensional
version of the Osirian symbol

00:07:23.310 --> 00:07:25.490 align:middle line:84%
starts with the
vector equilibrium,

00:07:25.490 --> 00:07:29.220 align:middle line:84%
a perfectly balanced force
field with 12 equal energy

00:07:29.220 --> 00:07:31.400 align:middle line:90%
lines radiating out.

00:07:31.400 --> 00:07:34.955 align:middle line:84%
They stabilize its center
like the 12 spokes of a wheel.

00:07:34.955 --> 00:07:39.280 align:middle line:90%


00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:42.200 align:middle line:84%
The primary pattern of
balanced energy flow

00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:44.480 align:middle line:84%
around this structure
is the torus.

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:50.630 align:middle line:90%


00:07:50.630 --> 00:07:53.500 align:middle line:84%
Here we expand to
the next larger scale

00:07:53.500 --> 00:07:56.463 align:middle line:84%
with a total of 64
pyramids called tetrahedra.

00:07:56.463 --> 00:08:02.010 align:middle line:90%


00:08:02.010 --> 00:08:04.550 align:middle line:84%
If we then put spheres
in representing

00:08:04.550 --> 00:08:06.530 align:middle line:84%
the toroidal energy
field surrounding

00:08:06.530 --> 00:08:13.220 align:middle line:84%
each of the pyramids and then
we drop away the pyramids,

00:08:13.220 --> 00:08:16.570 align:middle line:84%
we end up with a matrix
that is, amazingly,

00:08:16.570 --> 00:08:20.070 align:middle line:84%
an exact overlay for
the Osirian icon,

00:08:20.070 --> 00:08:22.680 align:middle line:84%
a three-dimensional model
of the same pattern that

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:25.810 align:middle line:84%
was burned into the rock
wall of the Egyptian temple

00:08:25.810 --> 00:08:27.210 align:middle line:90%
thousands of years ago.

00:08:27.210 --> 00:08:28.860 align:middle line:90%


00:08:28.860 --> 00:08:32.900 align:middle line:84%
Now we travel across
continents, from Egypt to China,

00:08:32.900 --> 00:08:36.840 align:middle line:84%
where the same geometry appears
at another sacred site built

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:38.710 align:middle line:90%
in 1420.

00:08:38.710 --> 00:08:41.480 align:middle line:84%
>>HARAMEIN: Then you go
to the Forbidden City

00:08:41.480 --> 00:08:44.059 align:middle line:90%
where the sun gods reside.

00:08:44.059 --> 00:08:47.892 align:middle line:84%
And where you find that
the ancients, the fu

00:08:47.892 --> 00:08:51.580 align:middle line:84%
dogs, the guardians
of the knowledge--

00:08:51.580 --> 00:08:55.060 align:middle line:84%
they guard the knowledge
under their paw.

00:08:55.060 --> 00:08:56.630 align:middle line:90%


00:08:56.630 --> 00:09:00.320 align:middle line:84%
>>F. GAMBLE: The same
geometry of 64 energy units

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:02.260 align:middle line:90%
is encoded again.

00:09:02.260 --> 00:09:04.830 align:middle line:84%
I started wondering, is
it just a coincidence

00:09:04.830 --> 00:09:06.900 align:middle line:84%
that the exact
same design appears

00:09:06.900 --> 00:09:09.035 align:middle line:84%
in significant places on
two different continents?

00:09:09.035 --> 00:09:10.500 align:middle line:90%


00:09:10.500 --> 00:09:14.620 align:middle line:84%
But then Nassim showed me
that this geometry of 64

00:09:14.620 --> 00:09:18.350 align:middle line:84%
is encoded time and again in
cultures across the centuries

00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:19.569 align:middle line:90%
and from all over the world.

00:09:19.569 --> 00:09:20.402 align:middle line:90%
[END VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:09:20.402 --> 00:09:22.560 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You could actually
see the Gaiam logo

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:25.140 align:middle line:90%
within that symbol as well.

00:09:25.140 --> 00:09:28.370 align:middle line:84%
>>K. GAMBLE: It's funny to watch
the clips because it really

00:09:28.370 --> 00:09:32.420 align:middle line:84%
speaks to-- some
people naturally see

00:09:32.420 --> 00:09:35.870 align:middle line:84%
the geometry of space and are
interested in these patterns.

00:09:35.870 --> 00:09:39.880 align:middle line:84%
And I came into this more
with sort of a social justice

00:09:39.880 --> 00:09:40.570 align:middle line:90%
orientation.

00:09:40.570 --> 00:09:42.590 align:middle line:84%
And what's the
ramifications on people?

00:09:42.590 --> 00:09:44.240 align:middle line:84%
And how does all
this fit together?

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:44.870 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What's it mean to me?

00:09:44.870 --> 00:09:45.220 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:09:45.220 --> 00:09:47.428 align:middle line:84%
>>K. GAMBLE: And what does
this mean to human beings?

00:09:47.428 --> 00:09:49.670 align:middle line:84%
And even in unpacking
what does it

00:09:49.670 --> 00:09:52.380 align:middle line:84%
look like-- we were so grateful
to work with Liquid Buddha

00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:55.070 align:middle line:90%
Studios to do these graphics.

00:09:55.070 --> 00:09:57.980 align:middle line:84%
To actually show and give
a chance for those of us

