proper relationship

00:18:43.170 --> 00:18:45.820 align:middle line:84%
between the chairman of the Fed
and a President of the United

00:18:45.820 --> 00:18:46.319 align:middle line:90%
States?

00:18:46.319 --> 00:18:47.049 align:middle line:90%


00:18:47.049 --> 00:18:48.590 align:middle line:84%
>>ALAN GREENSPAN:
Well, first of all,

00:18:48.590 --> 00:18:51.410 align:middle line:84%
the Federal Reserve is
an independent agency.

00:18:51.410 --> 00:18:55.280 align:middle line:84%
And that means,
basically, that there

00:18:55.280 --> 00:18:58.910 align:middle line:84%
is no other agency
of government which

00:18:58.910 --> 00:19:01.240 align:middle line:84%
can overrule actions
that we take.

00:19:01.240 --> 00:19:03.148 align:middle line:90%


00:19:03.148 --> 00:19:06.010 align:middle line:84%
There is no other
agency of government

00:19:06.010 --> 00:19:08.395 align:middle line:84%
which can overrule
actions that we take.

00:19:08.395 --> 00:19:09.490 align:middle line:90%


00:19:09.490 --> 00:19:11.490 align:middle line:84%
>>CATHERINE AUSTIN FITTS:
We have a private bank

00:19:11.490 --> 00:19:14.460 align:middle line:84%
that prints money on
behalf of the treasury.

00:19:14.460 --> 00:19:17.820 align:middle line:84%
The Federal Reserve prints
money on a debt-based system

00:19:17.820 --> 00:19:18.850 align:middle line:90%
which creates scarcity.

00:19:18.850 --> 00:19:20.060 align:middle line:90%


00:19:20.060 --> 00:19:24.160 align:middle line:84%
But it puts a group of insiders
in a position of having access

00:19:24.160 --> 00:19:27.610 align:middle line:84%
to all the data about the
economy when we don't.

00:19:27.610 --> 00:19:29.660 align:middle line:84%
So you have a small
group of bankers

00:19:29.660 --> 00:19:32.520 align:middle line:84%
who understand the data on how
the money works in the economy.

00:19:32.520 --> 00:19:36.150 align:middle line:84%
And it gives them the ability
to print money in a way

00:19:36.150 --> 00:19:39.910 align:middle line:84%
that the insiders are protected
and everybody else is drained.

