00:19:45.310 --> 00:19:46.530 align:middle line:90%
Is that really a possibility?

00:19:46.530 --> 00:19:48.750 align:middle line:90%


00:19:48.750 --> 00:19:51.460 align:middle line:84%
>>K. GAMBLE: Well, I think
that the evidence is there.

00:19:51.460 --> 00:19:54.240 align:middle line:84%
