we really unpack it.

00:19:56.180 --> 00:20:00.080 align:middle line:84%
Because it's so
socially challenging

00:20:00.080 --> 00:20:02.700 align:middle line:84%
just to talk about
notions of conspiracy.

00:20:02.700 --> 00:20:07.120 align:middle line:84%
But when you just understand
it and how it works, and you

00:20:07.120 --> 00:20:11.770 align:middle line:84%
understand a need-to-know
pyramid structure of how it is,

00:20:11.770 --> 00:20:14.910 align:middle line:84%
you can see it operate in
little ways and in big ways.

00:20:14.910 --> 00:20:18.300 align:middle line:84%
And I think the main point is
that the reason that we follow

00:20:18.300 --> 00:20:22.040 align:middle line:84%
the money, the reason
that we expose the banking

00:20:22.040 --> 00:20:25.260 align:middle line:84%
elite and the
conspiracy that we do

00:20:25.260 --> 00:20:28.950 align:middle line:84%
is because it informs us so that
we can have leverage solutions.

00:20:28.950 --> 00:20:31.260 align:middle line:84%
We're not just
looking for bad news

00:20:31.260 --> 00:20:32.650 align:middle line:90%
