it so everyone on this planet

00:21:12.040 --> 00:21:14.240 align:middle line:84%
has a chance to
thrive, it's going

00:21:14.240 --> 00:21:15.760 align:middle line:84%
to take more than
a little tweaking.

00:21:15.760 --> 00:21:18.410 align:middle line:84%
And recognizing that is
a way that we can now

00:21:18.410 --> 00:21:21.640 align:middle line:84%
