00:21:31.950 --> 00:21:33.700 align:middle line:84%
come to the
understanding that I have

00:21:33.700 --> 00:21:36.650 align:middle line:84%
in the course of making
"Thrive" than I ever did before.

00:21:36.650 --> 00:21:38.501 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Which is why
