00:22:32.450 --> 00:22:35.100 align:middle line:84%
invading their body, their
finances, their family,

00:22:35.100 --> 00:22:36.100 align:middle line:90%
whatever.

00:22:36.100 --> 00:22:39.790 align:middle line:84%
